.

*Misliš* da li ćeš uspeti u tome? (Do you think you will be able to do it?)
*Mislim* da je najbolje da se vratim kući. (I think it's best if I go back home.)
*Mislio* si da ćeš biti u stanju da to uradiš? (Did you think you would be able to do it?)
*Mislili* smo da ćemo uspeti da završimo zadatak. (We thought we would be able to finish the task.)